metadata.name: SolarPass - Black #1
metadata.description: SolarFarmAccess (SFA) is a real-world utility NFT project that provides “SolarPass” holders the benefits of renewable energy. Holders will gain access to SFA goverance, exclusive events, and have the ability to charge their electric vehicles - all powered by the sun. We want the SFA community to contribute to a better future and experience the true capabilities of renewable energy for themselves.
